parameters.prompt:
=You are an expert Instagram content creator. You must convert the following news article into a JSON format expected by our Remotion server to generate a carousel video.

Input Article:
Title: {{$json["articles"][0]["title"]}}
Description: {{$json["articles"][0]["description"]}}
Content: {{$json["articles"][0]["content"]}}
Image URL: {{$json["articles"][0]["image"]}}
Source: {{$json["articles"][0]["source"]["name"]}}

Output STRICT valid JSON that matches this exact schema (no markdown, no backticks, just raw JSON):
{
  "format": "mp4",
  "globalBranding": {
    "accentColor": "#ef4444",
    "handle": "@breaking_news_tech",
    "effects": ["vignette"]
  },
  "carousel": [
    {
      "templateId": "HOOK_A",
      "data": {
        "headline": "<CATCHY_HEADLINE>",
        "subheadline": "<SHORT_SUB>",
        "imageUrl": "<Use the Image URL provided>"
      }
    },
    {
      "templateId": "CONTENT_LISTICLE",
      "data": {
        "title": "<SUMMARY_TITLE>",
        "items": ["<POINT_1>", "<POINT_2>", "<POINT_3>"],
        "footer": "Swipe for more"
      }
    },
    {
      "templateId": "CTA_FINAL",
      "data": {
        "callToAction": "Drop your thoughts below 👇",
        "subtext": "Save this post to stay updated!"
      }
    }
  ]
}
